This paper is primarily focused on face detection and alignment using deep learning algorithms, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of cascade convolutional neural networks, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves image processing and manipulation, which is a sub-topic of multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the use of weight parameter adjustment and convergence acceleration, which are techniques commonly used in neural networks (cs.NE).
